          if (traitKey == 'email_address') {
            traitKey = 'email';
          } else if (traitKey == 'address') {
            traitValue = [
              safeInnerText(element.nextElementSibling),
              safeInnerText(element.nextElementSibling.nextElementSibling)
            ].join(', ');
          }

          traits[traitKey] = traitValue;
